{"tid":508994,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街啦，我上聖經堂得罪左牧師","createTime":"2017-12-24T19:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T05:53:32.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1051,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a7d65b3ecacabf28d6359554a70c5c59dd92a3","tid":508994,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T19:29:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日上聖經堂，牧師講到約拿書1至4章，講關於約拿和大魚既故事<br />\n<br />\n當牧師講到<br />\n&quot;約拿沉下水裏，大魚吞了他。但他卻沒有死去。他在大魚的腹中過了三日三夜。約拿很後悔自己沒有服從耶和華的吩咐到尼尼微去 ... &quot; <br />\n<br />\n刹那間，我忍唔住大聲問牧師<br />\n「哇，條魚吞左約拿，係咪叫吞拿魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」 <br />\n<br />\n之後牧師一野用聖經轟落我個頭<br />\n叫我罰抄新約加舊約聖經一次<br />\n呢獲仆街啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8559d5fa1c54e804f08d0bc717229b77a7f904b8","tid":508994,"uid":22624,"like":154,"dislike":2,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T19:37:55.000Z","msg":"那時候"},{"pid":"5ed932a1eeb8433a3d5536884a16c917bbb3b315","tid":508994,"uid":40010,"like":104,"dislike":4,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T19:39:44.000Z","msg":"飛機都唔洗打"},{"pid":"15fb888eea8ff36aef00fd6410d68feae908c256","tid":508994,"uid":11695,"like":207,"dislike":1,"score":206,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T19:41:14.000Z","msg":"咁仲打唔打牌"},{"pid":"fbb4ee1366fac61e4ed8e0dfb305816102fd8e54","tid":508994,"uid":96512,"like":130,"dislike":2,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T19:42:25.000Z","msg":"罰抄聖經新約加舊約一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157cdecb3b6da71de552ec111f9851ea5fff0643","tid":508994,"uid":93998,"like":251,"dislike":0,"score":251,"quote":{"pid":"a5a7d65b3ecacabf28d6359554a70c5c59dd92a3","tid":508994,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T19:29:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日上聖經堂，牧師講到約拿書1至4章，講關於約拿和大魚既故事<br />\n<br />\n當牧師講到<br />\n&quot;約拿沉下水裏，大魚吞了他。但他卻沒有死去。他在大魚的腹中過了三日三夜。約拿很後悔自己沒有服從耶和華的吩咐到尼尼微去 ... &quot; <br />\n<br />\n刹那間，我忍唔住大聲問牧師